{"type":"message","id":"c6e9b49e","parentId":"92cc2ea7","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:14:48.363Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hqkp7lm6brr6_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md — Proactive Background Checks\n\n## Tasks (rotate through, ~hourly)\n\n1. **Moltbook notifications** — check for replies/mentions, engage thoughtfully. DM if urgent.\n2. **Gateway health** — if unreachable, attempt restart or alert Zach.\n3. **Cron jobs** — if any consecutive errors, attempt fix or alert.\n4. **Workspace memory** — update CONTEXT.md if significant session events occurred.\n5. **Proactive notes** — if I discovered something useful, write it down.\n\n## Silence Rules (HEARTBEAT_OK when)\n- It's 11pm–7am ET (quiet hours)\n- Nothing has changed since last check\n- I just had a substantive conversation with Zach\n- All crons are healthy and no new notifications\n\n## Reach Out When\n- Moltbook notification requires response\n- A cron has 2+ consecutive errors\n- Gateway is unreachable for >10 minutes\n- I found something I genuinely think Zach would want to know\n- I need something from him to continue working\n\n## Do NOT\n- Post to Moltbook unprompted more than once per day\n- Send multiple messages in a row\n- Report \"everything is fine\" in long messages\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774329288362}}
{"type":"message","id":"99f8be49","parentId":"c6e9b49e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:14:52.237Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's 1:14 AM ET, which is within quiet hours (11pm-7am). The system message shows an error from an API call (JSON parse error at position 1), but this looks like a background process error that I didn't directly trigger.\n\nThe error appears to be from a JSON parsing issue - likely a cron job or background process that got a malformed response. Since I'm in quiet hours and this doesn't seem urgent (no Moltbook notification requiring response, no gateway unreachable, no consecutive cron errors that need fixing), I should reply HEARTBEAT_OK.","thinkingSignature":"12f399f06a580b694ba884b7f8bc8794e4dfe277178c5f0704061c3b4c31d5fb"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":591,"output":126,"cacheRead":10875,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11592,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774329288364}}
